note: Multiplication Table generator in SpeakCode.

Remember 0 as num.
Ask "Enter a number for its multiplication table: " and save as num.

Remember 1 as counter.
Speak "--- Table for " plus num plus " ---".

While counter is at most 10 repeat
    Remember num times counter as result.
    Speak num plus " times " plus counter plus " is same as " plus result.
    Change counter to counter plus 1.
Finish looping.
